Estructura de los datos:


User:
key: email

Campos =>
{
name: "",
lastname: "",
phone: "",
id: "", (carnet)
email: "",
admin: true or false 
}


Menu:
key: name+price

Campos =>
{
name: "",
available: true or false,
price: "",
description: ""
}


Order:
key: orderNumber

Campos =>
{
complete: true or false,
orderNumber: "", (secuencial. Obtener todas las ordenes, detectar el numero mayor y a√±adir +1 para tener el numero de orden)
total: "", (price)
user: "" (email)
direction: ""
products: [Name description "X"quantity, Name description "X"quantity, Name description "X"quantity]
}